Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • by.zti.main.scanner.Command

  • public class Command
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a typical command for ConsoleScanner to work with. It contains all data necessary to identify and execute different parts of code.
    Since:
    ZTIU 1.0.1
    See Also:
    ConsoleScanner, Consumable
